{
  "stem": "15396.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, I've lived all over the world lately, and I've been-- I haven't been much in America.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went to an art school--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--called the Colarossi, and by chance, I got a scholarship there which helped considerably, I can tell you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I was wrestling, and making, you know, a fairly good living at that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, I did that from early age, and from the day my uncle said, give up football or leave home.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We saw some of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We saw some of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not so much from the French, actually.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have to tell you, my experience with the French wasn't-- I don't remember many disagreeable things at all.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were so nice and so kind to a foreigner, and I never saw any real anti-Semitic feelings there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But you did see it sometimes among-- and I hate to tell you, but sometimes among American students, not that we saw American students much.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they stuck together, and I don't remember if they were-- the Jews that I knew were not one, one with that clique, you know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The ones I saw were usually fairly successful and already-- and a few students.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Can you describe any anti-Semitism that you saw in Paris?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember somebody one time leaving the table when somebody came to the-- and making an-- making some-- not an anti-Semitic remark as we would have known it, an anti-Jewish remark, you know?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I got up and left the table, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we sat-- this man and I sat-- this young man and I sat at a table so they could watch us, so they could see us.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We sat there and had a wonderful time.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
